---
title: Garlic and Mushroom Chicken Noodles with crunchy peanuts
description: These noodles are filling, fresh and flavourful, featuring crunchy peanuts for texture and coriander for a hint of brightness. Chicken, mushrooms and tender green beans make up the base of this simple and delicious meal.
